すべてのクラス

クラス 説明
AppConfigurerAdapter
AppConfigurerAdapter is for validation
BaseController
BaseController is to get user info at controllers
BaseService<T>
Interface to handle data about T object
Conf
Constant (Message, return code, path, etc.)
FileLink
Model for file data.
FileLinkMapper
Interface for MyBatis to handle fileLink
FileLinkServiceImpl
Handle file object.
HomeController
Controller for the page to enter projects data and links data, files data
Link
Model for link data.
LinkMapper
Interface for MyBatis to handle link
LinkServiceImpl
Handle link object.
LogAspct
LogAspct is for output logs.
LoginController
Controller for the page to login
Project
Model for project data.
ProjectForm
Form for the project
ProjectMapper
Interface for MyBatis to handle project
ProjectServiceImpl
Handle project object.
PublishController
Controller for the page to publish some projects data and one user-setting
RegistController
Controller for the page to input user-account
User
Model for user-account data.
UserForm
Form for the user-account
UserMapper
Interface for MyBatis to handle user-account
UserServiceImpl
Handle user-account object.
UserSetting
Model for user-account data.
UserSettingController
Controller for the page to input user-setting
UserSettingForm
Form for the user-setting
UserSettingMapper
Interface for MyBatis to handle user-setting
UserSettingServiceImpl
Handle user-setting object.
UtilMapper
Interface for MyBatis to use general SQL
WebSecurityConfig
WebSecurityConfig is for security (login, authority, etc)
